  "body": "## Features\r\n\r\n- Add `tree.format` and `--tree-format` to append Minijinja-rendered object summaries in the tree view. (#141)\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\notree pods.json --tree-format '{{ namespace }}/{{ name }}'\r\n```\r\n- Upgrade various dependencies.\r\n\r\n## Fixes\r\n\r\n- check file size before reading to prevent OOM. (#134)\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* fix: check file size before reading to prevent OOM by @kimjune01 in https://github.com/fioncat/otree/pull/134\r\n* feat(tree): add minijinja template for object node descriptions by @jonasws in https://github.com/fioncat/otree/pull/141\r\n* build(deps): bump actions/checkout from 6 to 7 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/fioncat/otree/pull/139\r\n* build(deps): bump softprops/action-gh-release from 2 to 3 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/fioncat/otree/pull/131\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @kimjune01 made their first contribution in https://github.com/fioncat/otree/pull/134\r\n* @jonasws made their first contribution in https://github.com/fioncat/otree/pull/141\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/fioncat/otree/compare/v0.6.5...v0.7.0",
